snippet.title: Another Win for CAFE, Battle of Ideas and More Johnny Depp/Amber Heard News! | Week in Men's Rights
snippet.description:
Multistreaming with https://restream.io/

Join us on the Week In Men's Rights show as we look at positive gains made for men of the week! The Canadian Association for Equality will be opening the first dedicated shelter for fathers and children, Elizabeth Hobson's debate at the Battle of Ideas, the good news regarding the very public Johnny Depp/Amber Heard case, and more! Tune in @6pm Eastern!

Sources:

https://menandfamilies.org/

https://youtu.be/O2Ildj9J8TE

https://www.metro.news/amber-heard-taunts-johnny-depp-over-his-victim-of-abuse-claim/1901323/
